HEADWORD: Tutti-frutti
<hw>Tut"ti-frut`ti</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[It., lit., all
fruits.]</ety> <def>A confection of different kinds of preserved
fruits.</def> -- <def2><pos>a.</pos> <def>Flavored with, or containing,
various fruits.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
